OL,3,C'I want a fleet': Police van converted
OL,4,Cinto mobile music studio
OL,6,FAn independent radio station in
OL,7,FBristol has converted a police van
OL,8,Finto a mobile music studio to provide
OL,9,Fcreative opportunities for underserved
OL,10,Fcommunities.
OL,12,FIt's called 'TREAD' and has started
OL,13,Ftravelling across the city to offer
OL,14,Fyoung people free production
OL,15,Fworkshops, DJ lessons and recording
OL,16,Fsessions.
OL,18,FNoods Radio has been broadcasting for
OL,19,Ften years, and the team says it wants
OL,20,Fto give back to the community where it
OL,21,Fwas founded.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
