PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777903638
OL,3,C'I want a fleet': Police van converted
OL,4,Cinto mobile music studio
OL,6,FIt hopes to deliver hundreds of free
OL,7,Fworkshops over the coming months.
OL,9,FCo-director of Noods Levels, the
OL,10,Fradio's community interest company,
OL,11,FIzzy Cross said: "We want to take a
OL,12,Fstudio - with all the fun and people
OL,13,Fthat come with it - to communities who
OL,14,Fotherwise wouldn't get it, like rural
OL,15,Fspaces.
OL,17,F"If we can leave a legacy, we just
OL,18,Fwant to have a lot of fun whilst doing
OL,19,Fsomething really meaningful."
OL,26,@sD@ROU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
