OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777903638
OL,3,C'I want a fleet': Police van converted
OL,4,Cinto mobile music studio
OL,6,FShe added: "This has been born out of
OL,7,Fa need for youth clubs where there is
OL,8,Fa lack of resources. We've been
OL,9,Fwelcomed with open arms. It's been
OL,10,Foverwhelming.
OL,12,F"But we knew that this was going to be
OL,13,Fa success because we were genuinely
OL,14,Flistening to what people needed. I
OL,15,Fthink this is just the start. I'm
OL,16,Fhoping to have a few of these - to
OL,17,Fhave a fleet!"
OL,26,@nD@LOUyD@NO]
