PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777903638
OL,3,C'I want a fleet': Police van converted
OL,4,Cinto mobile music studio
OL,6,FThe van, which is described as an
OL,7,Findustry-standard music studio, was
OL,8,Fconverted from a Greater Manchester
OL,9,FPolice vehicle. TREAD has been
OL,10,Fwelcomed by youngsters who can play
OL,11,Ftheir own music and learn how to DJ.
OL,13,FIt comes after a long period of cuts
OL,14,Fto youth provision across the country,
OL,15,Fsomething the team are trying to
OL,16,Fremedy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
